<style src="./RacketView.css"></style>
<template src="./RacketView.html"></template>
<script>
    import ViewtitleComponent from '@/components/ViewtitleComponent/ViewtitleComponent.vue';

    export default {
        name: "RacketView",
        data() {
            return {
                areaName: "Racket",
                logo_link: "https://racket-lang.org/img/racket-logo.svg",
                links_list: [
                    { "link": "https://racket-lang.org/", title: "Оффициальный сайт" }
                ]
            }
        },
        components: {
            ViewtitleComponent
        },
        provide() {
            return {
                areaName: this.areaName,
                logoLink: this.logo_link,
                linksList: this.links_list,
            }
        }
    }
</script>
